### ZtbAi Step API Smoke Tests (use with VSCode REST Client or curl)

@base = http://127.0.0.1:9958/api/projects
@pid = demo_project

### 1) service-mode
GET {{base}}/{{pid}}/step/service-mode/status

###
POST {{base}}/{{pid}}/step/service-mode/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{ "mode": "ai" }

###
GET {{base}}/{{pid}}/step/service-mode/result


